All tasks complete. Here's a summary of the changes:

### Changes made

**`cmd/doubletake/player.go`**:
- Added `roleDisplayNames` map for Civilian/Undercover/Blank → 平民/卧底/白板 display labels
- Added `case game.MsgRole:` in the message loop that:
  - Parses `roleName|word` format with `strings.SplitN(msg.Payload, "|", 2)`
  - Shows `assigned token: 苹果 [平民]` for Civilian/Undercover
  - Shows `assigned token: [白板] — 你是白板` for Blank
  - Uses `disp.Data()` for disguised format output (works correctly in stealth mode)

**`cmd/doubletake/player_test.go`**:
- Replaced the broken `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesMultipleMessages` with 5 proper tests:
  - `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesRole_Civilian` — verifies `assigned token: 苹果 [平民]`
  - `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesRole_Undercover` — verifies `assigned token: 香蕉 [卧底]`
  - `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesRole_Blank` — verifies `assigned token: [白板] — 你是白板`
  - `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesRole_Stealth` — verifies no `[DATA]` tag in stealth mode
  - `TestRunPlayer_ReceivesMultipleMessages` — verifies ROLE + READY coexist peacefully

### Verification

- `go build ./...` — no errors
- `go vet ./...` — no errors
- All 14 player tests pass (11 existing + 4 new)
